com.datastax.oss.dsbulk.executor.api.writer

Interface BulkWriter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AsyncBulkWriter, AutoCloseable, ReactiveBulkWriter, SyncBulkWriter
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BulkExecutor, ReactorBulkExecutor
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractBulkExecutor, ContinuousReactorBulkExecutor, DefaultReactorBulkExecutor

    public interface BulkWriter
extends SyncBulkWriter, AsyncBulkWriter, ReactiveBulkWriter
    A bulk writer that operates in 3 distinct modes:
    1. Synchronous;
    2. Asynchronous;
    3. Reactive.
